name: Force Flyer
blurb: A fast paced and strategic game for iOS and Android. Fight through randomized galaxies to earn money and upgrade your ship!

rewards.reward: Thanks for the support! You'll receive an awesome pack of wallpapers for every device we can think of so that you can show off your love of Force Flyer.

As well as listed above, You will receive a copy of the premium game for Android and iOS! This will include all the premium content and full tablet support! If our goal for the PC, Mac & Linux version is reached, you will also receive DRM-free copies of the game for those platforms!

As well as listed above, you will also receive a custom Kickstarter-only ship in the game for both iOS and Android, as well as a Kickstarter-only expansion. This content will not be available any other way and we promise it will be awesome. You will also receive the album "Impeccable Micro" by Ensnare, the soundtrack to the game!

As well as listed above, you will receive your name in the credits PLUS a custom poster signed by the team AND stickers of the Force Flyer lizard and the logo (see the project description for the poster and stickers!) Please add 3 dollars for International backers.

As well as listed above, you will have a special creative say in Force Flyer. You will a part of a unique community of Force Flyer players who will be able to vote, give us feedback and help shape the game. This group will not grow beyond this initial  Kickstarter reward, so that those who believed in this game from the start will always be a part of it no matter how long it lasts. You will also be a part of the closed beta for the Android version as well as the PC, Mac & Linux closed betas (if we reach the over-funded goal). For more information please see the project details.\r\n\r\nALSO you will receive a t-shirt that shows you are a part of this team. We will be updating a mock-up of the shirt shortly. Please add 5 dollars for International backers.

As well as listed above, you will have access to a personal email that I will check very actively. If you ever have a problem with the game or want to communicate something to me or my brother and want to get a response very quickly, even for advice or questions about gameplay, this will allow you to do so!
As well as listed above, you will work with our artists to create your own ship that will appear in the game. You will be able to name it and decide its attributes!

As well as awards #1-6, you will be able to work with our artists and game designers to create your own enemy in the game. You will able to tell us what you want him to look like, how you want him to act and how he plans on destroying the Force Flyer!
As well as rewards #1-5, you will be able to work with the artists and gameplay designers to create both your own ship and your own enemy! You will be able to kill your own enemy with your own ship!
As well as listed above, you will become one of the 2 Executive Producers on the game. You will help us make decisions in the development process. You will also be credited!

As well as listed above, we will fly you to our studio to stay with us and learn about the development of the game. You will receive hand-drawn concept art from the game and just get to hang out with us for a weekend.
